Omnichannel Journey Solution Workflow

Review the solution workflow for creating an omnichannel journey in Marketing Cloud Engagement using data from Data Cloud.

STAGE DATA IN DATA CLOUD	CREATE AN OMNICHANNEL AUDIENCE IN DATA CLOUD	CONFIGURE JOURNEY SETTINGS IN MARKETING CLOUD ENGAGEMENT

Define match rules for Identity Resolution to relate separate Individuals
To prioritize values for Unified Individual, define Reconciliation Rules
To select the MobilePush SubscriberKey, create a Calculated Insight
	
Create a segment to qualify the correct Unified Individuals
Activate the audience with applicable contact points and attributes
	
Update the send relationship on the activated data extension
Configure journey entry to use the activated data extension audience
Configure journey settings to use the desired send address
Add consent or preference filters as needed
